{
  "texts": [
    "As consumers increasingly seek personalized products, including functional foods for specific health conditions and culturally relevant flavors.",
    "Such adaptive systems can enhance user satisfaction, improve health outcomes, and support clearer market segmentation.",
    "Despite significant advancements, gustatory research continues to face unique challenges that require tailored AI solutions.",
    "One of the foremost challenges is individual variability in taste perception.",
    "This variability is influenced by factors such as genetics, age, health conditions, and diverse cultural backgrounds (Reed et al. 2006)."
  ]
}